    </div>
    
    <div class="toc-ref">
    
        <ol class="toc"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#CSS%E4%BC%AA%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E4%BC%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0"><span class="toc-text">CSS伪类与伪元素</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BC%AA%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%88pseudo-class%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-text">伪类（pseudo-class）</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BC%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%88pseudo-element%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-text">伪元素（pseudo-element）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>
    
